  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00311', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-101-bceca813', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-02', NULL, 'essay', '位於都市計畫住宅區之既成巷道應如何估價？又如該宗土地嗣劃入都市更新單元
